        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fair Manufactured Housing Lending Act </strong></p> <p>This bill requires a manufactured or modular home retailer to comply with consumer mortgage protections, including those related to lending origination and conflicts of interest. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
